name: eatr
tagline: Find food around you right NOW.
body:
### Eatr
Find food around you right now. Eatr will find you the best restaurants around you FAST. Just open the app, pick one, and eat!

### Authors and Contributors
This app was originally created at AngelHack Toronto 2015 by Adrian Machado (@AdrianMachado), Francis Zhang (@fzhang3), Jack Mo (@jack-mo), and Tim Mui (@timmui).
